        <UserObject label="«abstract»&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;ItemCatalogo&lt;/b&gt;" mermaidId="n:ItemCatalogo" mermaidBaseStyle="swimlane;html=1;fontStyle=0;fontSize=16;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;horizontal=1;childLayout=stackLayout;startSize=72;horizontalStack=0;resizeParent=1;resizeParentMax=0;resizeLast=0;collapsible=0;marginTop=12;marginBottom=12;stackSpacing=0;swimlaneFillColor=light-dark(#ECECFF,#1f2020);whiteSpace=wrap;fillColor=light-dark(#ECECFF,#1f2020);strokeColor=light-dark(#9370DB,#cccccc);fontColor=light-dark(#333333,#cccccc);fontFamily=Trebuchet MS,Verdana,Arial,sans-serif;" mermaidBaseValue="«abstract»&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;ItemCatalogo&lt;/b&gt;" id="p3JOn6k9V1Liic5UQjBN-4">
